                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4398" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0619</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8665 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">悬崖边的心跳：星辉娱乐全产业链路上的并购之“栓”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Heartbeat on Edge of Cliff: ‘Thrombosis’ of Mergers and Acquisitions in Rastar Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧，潘佳琪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学悉尼工商学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">星辉娱乐</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分步并购；一揽子交易；扣非后净利润；经营现金流</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">multi-step transaction, package transactions, net profit after deduction, operating cash flow</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010年1月20日星辉车模在深交所创业板A股挂牌上市，成为粤东首家创业板上市公司，此后四年公司一直致力于稳固主营业务，加大研发投入的同时向前延伸产业链，股价于2014年达到顶峰。2014年3月，星辉车模正式更名为星辉互动娱乐股份有限公司。但随后股价却一直持续下跌，并且似乎再无反弹之势，2018年12月甚至跌破3元大关，这一现象引发投资者的一片质疑与恐慌。本案例重点介绍了星辉娱乐在2015年分步并购春天融合的事件，以及该并购对公司造成的业绩假象，以及净利润和经营现金流不匹配的矛盾困境。通过本案例的学习，一是让学员认识分步并购的过程中长期股权投资的会计处理及其对合并财务报表的影响；二是让学员能够掌握如何通过实质重于形式的职业判断对分步收购过程中企业的会计政策选择进行合理的分析和解读；三是引导学员思考应如何通过损益表的利润表象透视企业的真实的价值信息。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Rastar Group was listed on A-share market in 2010. Since then, the company has been committed to stabilizing its main business by increasing R&amp;D investment and extending its industrial chain. The stock price reached its peak in 2014. However, the stock price has continued to fall, and the stock price even fell below the 3 yuan mark in 2018. This phenomenon caused a lot of doubts and panic among investors. After briefly introducing the development process of Rastar Group, this case describes the dilemma that Rastar Group faces after 2014, which is the contradiction between performance growth and stock price decline, net profit and operating cash flow mismatch. It focuses on the event that Rastar Group twice purchased and sold Spring company in 2015. Through the case study, one aim is to let the students understand the development process of the whole industry chain enterprises; the other is to enable them to review the basic accounting knowledge of long-term equity investment and consolidated enterprise statements; the third is to guide the students to think about whether the investment income formed by mergers and acquisitions can be smoothly transformed into the endogenous growth of enterprises, thus helping enterprises stabilize stock prices.   </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长期股权投资、合并财务报表、所有者权益</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
